  "body": "In latest `master`, the chat view channels are rendered like this (probably applies to 1-on-1 chats as well):\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-09-30 08-42-32](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/193207179-f75186a6-75c8-4347-a057-31e759212fc1.png)\r\n\r\nNotice how they don't align with the search bar anymore\r\n\r\nFor comparison, this is what it looks like in the community view:\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-09-30 08-43-58](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/193207361-aea8a372-9684-41e2-9a30-59d3f6315849.png)\r\n\r\nAlthough, these two probably aren't meant to look identical.\r\n",
